legion-toolkit (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release for Linux
  * Full feature parity with Windows version including:
    - Power mode control (Quiet, Balanced, Performance, Custom)
    - Battery management (charge limits, conservation mode, rapid charge)
    - Thermal monitoring and fan control
    - RGB keyboard lighting with effects
    - Display refresh rate and color management
    - Automation profiles and rules engine
    - System tray integration
    - Comprehensive CLI interface
  * Support for legion-laptop kernel module
  * Multi-distribution support (Debian, Ubuntu, Fedora, Arch)

 -- Legion Toolkit Team <noreply@example.com>  Mon, 23 Sep 2025 00:00:00 +0000